column5: When Jack asked his beard if it would stop being so unruly, it replied, “I'm a braid knot.”
While exerting +1 Will, we will hear the lamentations of our enemies once they look upon your boss blonde braided beard.
Show the +1 Endurance to braid this sucker every morning and clean out the crumbs.
Give me an air of +1 Respect with a gray braid.
My bandmates will be green with envy when I show up to practice sporting this egregious green neck grass.  It shows a lot of Character.
It takes a lot of Confidence to sport this pink chin vine.  +1 to be exact.
If you can't get the beard you love, love the one you get.
Eyes will be smiling, when I wear with this courageous braid.
The teacher asked Javier how many of the whole numbers on the chalkboard were divisible by 2 to which Javier replied, “All of them.”
Keep my neck warm during those long sea voyages with Thor's neck thatch.
The King was frustrated with the ineptitude of his assassins.  When asked why they had been so unsuccessful at killing Count Heivaas Thevahn Dat, they replied simply, “Heivaas Thevahn Dat got away.”
I've noticed that our shipmates are all much more flexible now that I've hired a Pirates instructor.  +2 Flexibility for all!
Curiosity got the better of me, and now I've got a jolly, green goatee.
Maybe I shouldn't have trusted that red dye-bottle.
I can't wait to impress everyone with my new purple +1 Passion.
Spruce up the area under my mouth (for War).
Honesty is the best policy, and honestly, I look awesome with this beard.
This is nacho ordinary beard.  Be grateful for the +1 Gratitude
I'm happier than an invisible agoraphobic with my new beard.
Beware, it lives.
If Greenland is icy and Iceland is greeny, is Ireland happy?
Are the people that made grape gum aware that grape gum doesn't taste like grapes?
Four score and seven years ago, there were 350% less people.
You can wear a beard 24601 ways, but this is the only way you should.
It's a reasonable, short black beard for a reasonable person. In fact, I'm now +1 more Reasonable.
Yo, ho, ho and a bottle of dye.
Ooh!  I hope that this is the propeller kind!  Neeerrrrr, neeerrrrr!!!
It's not a manner of confidence of wearing a pink tie, it's a matter of fabulousness.
I'm readying my acceptance speech by tieing up in style.
Protect my modesty in style.  Antipuritic sold separately.
You can't hold no groove if you ain't got no pocket.  Maybe a +1 Patience will help me walk the bass a little better.
My beats will go over like a lead zeppelin.
Kum ba yah will never be the same, once it's played on this dreadnaught.
Experience 23 frets of solid-body, crunchination.
Take a musical journey with these 53 keys of purple prodigiousness.
Cower criminals with this cordon of courage!  +1 Justice will help them see the light.
This thing gets great gas mileage.
Wrangle those cheerleaders with the shrieking might of the Slyvie 61!
Namaste it in style.
Prove my loyalty to Bahá'u'lláh with beautiful Ba'hai.
Nothing will grant me serenity faster than following The Four Noble Truths.
As-Salam Alaikum.  No jokes here.  Just +1 Austerity
If I'm going to bear a cross, I might as well do it fashionably.
Wear a Magen David close to my heart.
Ain't nobody's business if I do wear this fine neckpiece.
Coming from the Western Urals, this amethyst is thought to ward off seductions.
This imported Sri Lankan gemstone commands respect from anyone that spies it.
I'll be getting blood from a stone in no time.  I just need +1 Focus to get it done.
Although uncommon, this stone was produced from the Brazilian mines and shines brightly.
While I hope that we're together for 60 years, I don't know if I can wait for our diamond anniversary to get such a fabulous necklace.
Not only does it bring out my eyes, but it get's me a +2 Courage, too!
I'm an extroverted type.  At least that's what the gypsy said.
It's a lot easier to be faithful when I get such a pretty necklace and +1 Fidelity.
It would be hard to conscientiously object to such a beautiful piece of jewelry.
I'll never forget how this necklace makes me feel.  It's +1 Encouraging, too.
Some say that the purpose of life is to end.  What say you?
Where did they get cornflower blue?  If somebody put some blue corn down in front of me, I'd be all, “You can take this right back to the kitchen and tell them to hold the blue.”
This tie will really bring out the red in my bloodshot eyes.
There's just something about a neat, clean tie that makes the outfit.  The +1 Cleanliness is just a bonus.
If we're going to go with this tie, keep orange far away from the rest of my outfit, please.
This Accessory, when equipped, will allow you to remove whatever is slung around my neck.
This ebony color will beguile my sad fancy into smiling.
If you ever feel like coloring my eyebrows, you can equip different shades in the Commissary.
While, I could get my roots done, I kind of like the way that I'm rocking the silver look.
It's only a matter of time before I try out the pink.  We might as well get this over with.
Nothing shouts non-conformist like somewhat original hair-color choices.
They say that blondes have more fun, but do they have +1 Character?
Let's just see if blondes have more fun.
This is my standard bubble.  Not too tall, not too short.
Spending all that time on the rack has finally paid off!
I just installed a drop ceiling in the basement.
If you're thinking about being my baby, it don't matter if you're black or white.
You can color my bubble by buying a different color with the Ethicals you've collected.  I'm partial to blue.
I need a weapon.  Maybe +4 Creativity will help me improvise in the firefight.
Light your darkest hour.
I won't even need the +1 Dignity wearing this shade.
Wort! Wort! Wort!
Voulez-vous me regardez ?  +1
Here comes the Sun.  Doo doo doo doo.
I can equip this set of peepers for a more elegant look.
This is the default set of eyes for me, your Conscience.  You can equip different eyes for me in the Commissary.
Being all moral all the time can be tiring.  It looks like I need some rest.
If the eyes are the window to the soul, then I've got floor-to-ceiling panes up in here.
These peepers are the next-best thing to night vision goggles.
I'm so tired.  I shouldn't have stayed up and watched that Nat Geo marathon.
In the Nerd-Geek-Dork Venn Diagram, eyewear falls in the intersection between Social Ineptitude and Obsession.
I should get a pair of spectacles to go with these beadie guys.  At least the +1 Grace will help me see a little better.
Irises are overrated.  I'd rather have one giant, evil looking pupil.
Whether I'm a Sven or an Allura, I love this blazing color.
Sha la la la la la la la la la dee dah.  Just like that.
Although as a Conscience, I don't need contacts, you can change my eye color in the Commissary.  This shade of green is my standard color.
Pinkeye!  LOL!
Even Cleopatra would fall for these eyes.
This color is more than meets the eye.  Every leader could use a little +1 Humility.
Do not let your effort to remain who you are limit you.
This is the purr-fect...  Wait, no, I'm not going to do that.
I'll bearly be able to contain your happiness sporting this look.
I'll be as loyal as your favorite pup, and I won't even puke in your shoes.
Oh man, this is a scary face!  I wonder what kind of dragon I'll be!  I hope I'm the poison kind.
Why the long face?
I'll be the proudest monkey that they'll ever see.  +5 Kinship will help me with the troop, too.
I don't think that you should be listening to your friends.  I don't need any bot-ox injections.
Without a snout, this is the best choice for selfless Consciences.
So, the boss comes in and asks  “Who moved my cheese?”  He looked me right in the face when he said that.  Can you believe that?
If I'm up at the crack of dawn already, I might as well pull a comb through my comb.
It's not a baaaad choice.
I'm always ready to listen to your dilemmas.  Don't let my companionship slither on the vine.
So, what kind of Virtue will this face instill?  Shere Kahnfidence.
While three wolves are better than one, I can still be the alpha with this look.
Eight Virtues, 3 Principles, a cloth map and a obsessed child.
Ganesha will most certainly assit you after I wear my Aum face.  +4 Prudence isn't bad, either.
I look like a rock star.  +4 Punctuality will help me get to the gig on time, too.
My mom always told me that if I kept making this face, it would stick.  I'm okay with that, really.
I remembered to cross my T this time.
Do you see how my brow and nose form a crucifix!  Check the out!
Honor my heritage with the meshugenah sheild.
We got some girl-power all up ins.
Show them who wears the pants around here.  Wait, I don't have any legs.
You wouldn't hit a Conscience with glasses one, would you?
Nobody will be as ironic or iconic as I will be sporting these frames.
I won't be fishing for compliments anymore.
There's more to this symbol that what appears here.  But, if I showed the whole thing, I doubt you'd be reading this right now.
Accentuate my chakra and unleash my +5 Wisdom with this respectable decoration.
Look!  The little kirpans make a moustache!
All cows eat grass when every good boy does fine.
This face is fun, fun, fun, fun.  I'm looking forward to the weekend.
Equip this as my face to remove any other markings.
objc_exception_throw - Null Pointer Exception – Expected Humor +1 Awareness
Gaia and I are peas in a pod.  This will add to my Character
Frida and Bert aren't the only ones that can rock the unibrow.
There's nothing greater than this face.
My face will glow with the light of knowledge.  The cat isn't the only thing that Curiosity killed.
This face is integral to my look.
Keep my intentions pure by blessing me with this reverent symbol.
Try to keep Discipline between my darkness and lightness with this face.
There was a song joke here originally, but with my +7 Encouragement, I got the developer to remove it.
Only the most dignified of Consciences will sport this look.
This face will do in a pinch.  Maybe I can meet a nice Pisces while I'm at it.
Am I a goat?  Am I a fish?  Either way, I'm totally delish.  Joking aside, this gives me a +7 Austerity.
Why be one-faced, when you can be two-faced?
Show them my GRR face.
Show some +7 Balance with the scale face.
As a water sign, I roll with the punches... now if only fish could punch back.
What did the archer say to the optometrist?  I got a bulls-eye.
Did you know a scorpion's butt is on it's tail?  Man, what an unpleasant appendage.
Like a bull in a china shop, I'll be extra Persistent with this face.  +7 to be exact.
I'm touched (for the very first time), that you would get me such a lovely face.
I can do the boogie woogie or just get juiced in style with these shades.
This is the default mouth for me.  You can purchase other more decorative grills in the Commissary.
There's a fine line between pouty lips and trouty lips.
Don't leave me fangin', I've got to have this mouthpiece.
I just really need to get to the dentist.
Administer with grace with this organizational accoutrement.
Never Bflat again with this licorice stick.  It sings, sings, sings.
I'll belt out some sensitive songs on Karaoke night.
I'll never E flat again with such a sultry horn.  With +5 Flexibility, I can now sit in on any set.
I think to myself, 'What a wonderful horn.'  Blow out a crazy riff with +5 Spontenaity
Win first chair this this excellent viola.  First chairs can do well with a +5 Punctuality.
Take me out to the ballgame.
Make a break with this regulation beater.
I'll have an aviary of Eagles, Birdies and Condors when you take up the Golden Boar.
The Putt will let me hit the cup with your eyes closed.  +1 Focus supplied!
I'll be racking up the hat tricks with this stick.
Join the row crew and get busted for drunk and dis-oar-derly all at the same time.
I 40 love this racquet.  I just came up with that thanks to the +2 Spontenaity.
The heft of this instrument of dismemberment allows for easy separation of body parts from the body-whole.
I can down my prey with compassion with the U4.
I'll be striking down bad guys, fast and loose with this circlet of death.
Hook those pesky sheep  in no time!  As a humble shepherd, I could use the +1 Humility.
While lesser Gladiators might wield more extravagant weapons, I like to defer to simple, tempered steel.
Don't baste your enemies.  Maul them.
I place my +5 Trust in this sword, and you should, too.
Don't try running away, because you're the one I will find.
I went down to Kirpan Alley.  It was the roughest place I'd ever been.  They were hitting each other with 2x4's, and I was like, “Hey!”.
This is my rifle.  This is my gun.  This is for fighting.  This is is for fun.
I'll cleave through my enemies with verve when I yield this scintillating scimitar.
The next time someone gets in my face, I can whip this out and yell, “You can spear me the details!”
Not all those who wander are lost.  Add to my Balance with a +1.
Whether I'm ruling under the sea or under the earth, I'll command attention with this leister.
If you equip this Accessory, it will allow you to remove whatever I'm holding on either side.
This bag really brings out the blue in my eyes.
Don't feel bad about the animal skin, it's digital animal skin.
I may not be a baglady, but I want that fabulous bag, Lady.
With a +3 Thrift, it's nice to have a gray bag.
I can't wait to strut around the home screen with this bag over my shoulder.
Oh, my girlfriends are going to be green with envy.
I don't need an 8 way mirror to see how gorgeous this bag is.
I can't wait to find some cute pumps to go with this bag.  Now all I need are some legs.
You know we totally have to get the bow, too, right?
I like to sheath my sword in style.  +2 Respect.  Now, all we need is the Katana.
Protect me from those errant back stabbings with the Razorback.  It's good for frontal abuse, too!
Unleash some excessive force with this tonfa.  Our enemies will be blinded by +2 Justice.
Stop calling.  Stop calling.  I don't want to talk anymore.
Express my inner imp with this tail augmentation.
Don't forget my riding crop.  In all seriousness, we should get the Horse Face to go along with this +5 Austerity.
I'm-a strut my stuff with this fluffy scut.  You know what they say about rabbits, so I'll need the +2 Kinship.
This little piggy isn't going to market.
I can't wait to prove my Loyalty with such a trim tail.
Do you think that I can lead this orchestra?  You can baton it.
(Fictional) studies show that placing a pencil behind your ear makes you appear with +1 Aptitude.
You are now a budding Morathologist and have attained the rank of Monad.  Your days as the FNG are behind you.
You have become Literate in the ways of a Monad.  Being able to see the humor in most situations will serve you well.
You must have had to make a distasteful choice to reach Novice.  Let's be thrifty in our unethical behavior!
A Morathology Novice Rank, Literate Class has just been bestowed upon you.  You are like a ethical tadpole eager to change up your immoral little tail for some conscientious froglegs.
As a Novice Morathologist, you have shown the ability to complete a task quickly.
You have achieved the rank of Observer by seeing that most moral situations are not black and white.
You have become Literate in the ways of a Observer.  Being honest with oneself and others will make the path to a MoraLife easier.
You have Lettered as a Observer.
You have proven yourself a Legendary Observer.  Your professional Morathology career awaits.
You are now a Professional Morathologist.
Congratulations on making Query.  It's the question that drives us.
You have proven your literacy in the Querical ways.
Now that you've returned the MoraLife, you have achieved the Rank of Revenant.
You have become Literate in the ways of a Revenant.
You have Lettered as a Revenant.
Your education, while never complete, is ample.  You now take up the mantle of Morathology Steward.
You have become Literate in the ways of a Steward.
You have Lettered as a Steward.
You have proven yourself a Legendary Steward.
With your impressive skills, you can now see both sides of every argument.  You have become a Morathologist Wizard.  Let the world change under your influence.
You have become the change you wished to see in the world.  Welcome to the ranks of the Legendary Moral Wizards.
Bring a little sunshine into my afterlife.
A rose by any other name, isn't called a rose anymore.
Hey, Blanco Niño!  Watch out for the SAAAAAAAAck.
My sinkers will fall off the table with this rock.
Own the paint with Willson's Traveller.
When was the last time you held a real bowling ball?
Point:  The best defense is a good offense.  Counterpoint:  Then why do you need offense?
Give 'em the ole fishhook.
Why don't they just sell walkers with the tennis-balls pre-applied?
Spruce up my deserted island with the Survivor!
Good software should not need explanation, aside from the 3000 help screens you've probably seen by now.
They say diamonds are a girl's best friend, but I've never had a diamond offer to pick me up from the airport.
My heart will turn hoops if you buy me these bojangles.
Just think.  It takes an imperfection to make something so perfect.
I know that I don't have ears, but I can't help wanting such beautiful jewelry.

column2: Triple S Stainless Steel Stud Earring
column5: I'll feel like a stud when I sport this stud.
So, when I finish my roll, will you run it up to the pharmacy to get my prints?
Only someone of wealth and taste would be able to discern the craftsmanship of this mug.
The stream and pool is wet and cool: So nice for feet! And now we wish to catch a fish, So juicy-sweet!
Whether you're looking to measure molarity or morality, the Beerman is the right choice.
Whatever happened to Jumpman?  +1 Happiness.
I don't have a respectful place to put these when they're not in use.  So, I guess I'll just have to use them all the time.
Don't let Kislev pass me by without lighting up.
I'll painting happy little clouds now that I've got +1 Creativity.
Look at his little crown.  He's super-strong king.  Yes, he is!
I, too, can form an independent nation with this patented plumage.
Honor the faith with repeated prayer.
Mete out tolerance and justice with this regal staff.  (It also has a secret compartment that holds candy.)
Why would there be a syringe here for sale?  What good could that possibly do?  It's not like it's even an insulin syringe.  I'm going to have to talk to them about this.
I can see my house from here!
Never lose another duel with this boomstick.
Taste the tannins in this lovely, full-bodied reserve.
I'm not really a white wine kinda Conscience, but I'll dabble a bit if the year was good.
When you absolutely have to get into that burning building, no other tool will do.  The +1 Confidence doesn't hurt either.
I'm totally not going to make any hammer jokes.  This is just a really fine tool.
This highly sought-after landscaping tool is effective in urban, suburban and rural environments.  Security device sold separately.
Do you see that nice, smooth, even bevel up there on the wood at the top of the screen?  I used this handsaw to do it.  That's right.
This one time, I was at the block party with my sisters during Rush.  We totally all woke up with each others' underwear on the next day.
Never leave port without your trusty navigational device.  Person-whom-can-actually-read-it sold separately.
There once were four walls, orthogonal.  A vision? a place that was octagonal.  I whipped out a square.  Octagon-table laid bare.  Now finding 90 degrees?  Improbable.
Don't let the cream set out too long.  Whisk it.
Equipping this Accessory will allow you to remove whatever I've got on top of my head.
Augment my olfactory senses with these setaceous sensors.  I'll get a +1 Awareness, too!
Without any licensing agreements pending, I hope that you like a plain, red baseball cap.
As a token of Team Axe's appreciation to its beta testers, everyone gets a free baseball cap in humble Lancer colors.
I'm not exactly sure what the purpose of a propeller hat is.  It is not able to generate sufficient lift to get me off the ground.
Reduce my drag coefficient with this aerodynamic brain pan.  Woo!
Whip up a batch of Flappen-jacken, with this culinary accessory.
Protect my noggin from out-of-control rebar cages with this construction helmet.
Part of being a just Ruler is being able to chose between Imperial and Metric.
Uneasy lies the head that wears the crown.  Maybe +10 Compassion will ease my Conscience.
I'd better watch out with this cap, I'll put somebody's eye out.
What did you say?  I can't hear you over the sound of how awesome these ears are.
I can be ready to respond to the slightest sound with such an increase in auditory area.
If curiosity killed the cat, but cats have nine lives, curiosity better watch the *%@>? out.
As a registered Morathologist, I'll always impress with this titian tarboosh.
They won't let me push the siren until I wear the hat.
Football.  Serious bidness.  But, +1 Passion is required, too.
Protect my eyes with the Goggles.  Protect my outlook with the +1 Hope.
Teacher seeks pupil, must have an earnest desire to save the world.
I'll feel like the queen of the pride with this mane.
What would you do for a Blond Ike?
Whether I'm walking down the runway or across the palace grounds, I'll catch their eyes with these auburn braids.
I'm going to put up my hair, and get ready to flex mystuff.  It's even got a +1 Flexibility.  What a coincidence!
I'll have to find a nice pair of stockings to go along with this cut.
Isn't she lovely?  Isn't she wonderful?
This took all morning to do, but I think that it's worth it.
It's so much easier to get the part down the middle of the scalp perfect when you're bald.
Enjoy the sound of silence when people gasp at this mane.
Don't let anyone tell you that hope is a dangerous thing.  Be persistent.
I see you driving round town the cut I love, and I'm like, “Forget you.”
Are you gonna go this way?
The sky won't be the only thing I'll be kissing after getting coiffed up with this natural.
While the college at Baraboo is closed, you can still be an entertainer if you've got the right look.
Keeping up this slick style is serious business.  I'll need the +1 Austerity.
What IS in a 6 demon bag?  It looks like it's +1 Confidence.
I won't have a problem finding somebody to love when I get this cut.
Why so serious?
Forget the new car and caviar, pony up for this four star daydream hairdo.
You can't have the haircut if you don't love the haircut.
Pickup a pizza, a pineapple and a ham.  We're going to have a good time.
This cut's got everything that Uncle John needs.
Patience is a Virtue, and so is applying the gel it takes to prop up this mop.
Abstain from re-coloring this shock of green.
Curiosity will get the better of those that spy this pink pompadour.
Stand up my violet locks with +1 Confidence.
Red Rover, Red Rover send a barber right over.
Come Halo or high water, I'll be the talk of the town sporting this nimbus.
Protect my eyes with this last line of sweat defense.
Never fear a high-sticking when equipped with the Bassman.
If I'm going to be bad, you might as well own it with this skull augmentation.
What a sweet smell this leaf gives off!  It has a calming affect on me.  +1 Serenty to be exact.
Administer to the infirm and wretched in style.
I can be both an Officer and a gentleman with this cap up top.  The +1 Balance is just a perk.
Tonight, I'm going to party like it's a century ago.
Anchors aweigh and say farewell to foreign shores by tipping the Dixie Cup 65.
Keep every one guessin' about your intention.
This equipment will have my enemies screaming, 'Game Over, Man!'
Whether I'm splitting rails or giving speeches, I'll display at least +1 Character donning this noggin topper.
Protect my hair from the desert air with this righteous wrapping.
Shield my head from Loki's nets with this pronged skull protector.
I'll be defying gravity once I don this chartreuse chapeau.
All we have to decide is what to do with the awesome hat that is given us.
Put on your Yarmulke.  It's time for Chanukah.
